gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Timberwolves 121, Trail Blazers 109
gameRecap.excerpt: Anthony Edwards leads the Timberwolves with 41 points (16-27 FG) and four 3PM as they defeat the Trail Blazers, 121-109. Rudy Gobert added 16 points and 15 rebounds in the victory, while Anfernee Simons tallied 20 points, five assists and four 3PM for the Trail Blazers in the losing effort. The Timberwolves improve to 38-16 on the season, while the Trail Blazers fall to 15-38.
